{"tid":1182647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解反送中","createTime":"2019-06-02T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T10:38:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a518f98701c8a8190ece9724ec7113222f58a6cd","tid":1182647,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190602/20693781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693781&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIy6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=566da37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693781&h=5f6c20a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190602/20693781</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解反送中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190602/large/02la3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F02la3p5.jpg&h=76bfb8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「香港野豬關注組」幹事黃豪賢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「香港野豬關注組」幹事黃豪賢<br />\n<br />\n我們每年都會返大陸反對玉林狗肉節和某些主題樂園的動物表演，亦經常批評內地供港豬隻運輸過程虐畜，動保人士很大機會已觸犯內地法律。我們擔心修例後會因批評動物福利而被控顛覆國家、尋釁滋事罪，再被引渡返大陸受審。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190602/large/02la2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F02la2p8.jpg&h=0278c611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教育大學社會科學系講師黎明<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育大學社會科學系講師黎明<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例令社會氛圍充滿白色恐怖，這將明顯扼殺香港的言論自由、結社自由及政治空間，甚至有機會影響學術自由。修例如同在香港的法治人權保障上撕開一個裂口，使其暴露於不公正不透明不人道的司法制度之下。 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n內地多潛規則 中小企憂踩地雷"}]}